<h2 class="bold font-l">A Small Memento Of Mexico</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Diego gives Rafael the Zorro Mark on his neck so he'll never forget him. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AScarToRemember" class='trope-example-link'>A Scar to Remember</a></p>
</div>
